data.title: PsiloCybian - Peyotl
data.description:
Prepare yourself for real psytrance treat as Neogoa unleashes the new PsiloCybian album, Brain Dissolver! After the release of two full-length albums on Ovnimoon Records, Croatian psytrance producer Saša Dukić returns to Neogoa, where he has already appeared with his side project Screw Loose on the Dimensional Gateway series of compilations. Each of the ten tracks featured on this release were carefully crafted in his studio and tested on many dance floors around Europe—and now they are finally available for your enjoyment! All tracks are written and produced by Saša Dukić, except track #6, written and produced by Saša Dukić and Igor Čeranić. Mastering by Igor Čeranić at Deimos Soundlabs, with artwork design by Liquid Media.

01 - Sponge (145 BPM) 
02 - The Creator (145 BPM) 
03 - Reality Bomb (145 BPM) 
04 - Integrated Circuits (142 BPM) 
05 - Brain Dissolver (145 BPM) 
06 - Spooky Doobi Doo (vs Deimos) (145 BPM) 
07 - Interconectedness (145 BPM) 
08 - Human Show (142 BPM) 
09 - Peyotl (135 BPM) 
10 - Strange Place to Play (100 BPM)

Free download: http://www.ektoplazm.com/free-music/psilocybian-brain-dissolver
